            <q>functions of examining, inspecting, reviewing or studying the financial or other management of the public body".</q>
            Under the wording, it is still possible that there would be some concerns.</p><p>
            One of the questions that I put to the Minister&#x2014;I forgive him for not being able to answer it&#x2014;is whether there had been definitional difficulties or issues arising under the <a href="/acts/government-resource-and-accounts-act-2000">Government Resource and Accounts Act 2000</a>. I would be interested to know whether the
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_7gc' title='Col. 7GC &mdash; HL Deb 23 February 2004 vol 658 c7GC' name='column_7gc' href='#column_7gc' rel='bookmark'>7GC</a>
            Minister's officials could look into the matter and write to Members of the Committee to see how the definition works in practice.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0658P0-00807'>
        <a name='S5LV0658P0_20040223_GCR_31'>  </a>
