          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_10gc' title='Col. 10GC &mdash; HL Deb 23 February 2004 vol 658 c10GC' name='column_10gc' href='#column_10gc' rel='bookmark'>10GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-00829'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040223_GCR_53' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        4.3 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0658P0-00830'>
        <a name='S5LV0658P0_20040223_GCR_54'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-michael-allenby' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040223_GCR_54' title='Link to this speech by Mr Michael Allenby' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
