            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_23gc' title='Col. 23GC &mdash; HL Deb 23 February 2004 vol 658 c23GC' name='column_23gc' href='#column_23gc' rel='bookmark'>23GC</a>
            simply attempts to transfer the functions in relation to Welsh education bodies to the Auditor General for Wales.
          </p>
